Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:01.00,0:00:10.00,Lyrics0,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,字幕檔修正：Clive
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:27.33,0:00:29.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,覺得這棟大廈怎麼樣？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:29.49,0:00:31.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是涼爽的地方吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:31.97,0:00:32.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:48.45,0:00:50.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,妳是特別的一個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:51.33,0:00:57.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在我的狂熱者俱樂部裡\N那些傢伙都不知道有這大廈呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:01.65,0:01:08.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們這些令人作嘔的\N粗俗的，自大的，愚鈍的，沒用的名人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:09.25,0:01:12.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只是因為你有幾個電視演出
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:12.77,0:01:14.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,知不知羞恥啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:14.29,0:01:17.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,以為自己是甚麼大人物啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:17.29,0:01:17.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要臉…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:17.89,0:01:18.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,混蛋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:21.73,0:01:24.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,被一個愚鈍沒用的名人踢\N的感覺如何？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:24.53,0:01:26.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,妳這老母狗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:27.57,0:01:31.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,妳這惡臭的香水使我感到難受
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:32.13,0:01:34.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,讓人作嘔的是妳才對啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:59.01,0:02:02.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我將要控告你…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:03.57,0:02:07.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我…我兒子是個…優秀的律師
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:08.61,0:02:12.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,像你這樣的年輕人\N將會像一隻臭蟲般被壓碎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:13.09,0:02:15.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,聽到了沒有？年輕人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:02.00,0:03:16.00,Lyrics0,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,A KITE カイト [Uncut Edition]
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:11.00,0:03:16.00,Lyrics1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,[第一話]
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:24.37,0:03:28.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們找到兩顆彈頭…\N一顆在胸腔，一顆在腦袋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:29.09,0:03:30.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,依皮膚下血的痕跡來看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:34.61,0:03:35.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,應該是當場死亡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:36.29,0:03:37.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,赤井先生…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:38.45,0:03:41.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這該是一支很特別的槍…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:41.97,0:03:44.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,子彈在體內爆炸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:48.77,0:03:50.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,最好檢查一下子彈碎片
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:51.97,0:03:53.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,醫療隊還在這裡嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:53.89,0:03:56.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因為食物中毒，他們全都在醫院
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:56.37,0:03:58.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那些沒用的傢伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:58.93,0:04:00.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,浪費了納稅的銀子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:01.41,0:04:02.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那個婆婆呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:03.89,0:04:05.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是驚嚇過度而死的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:06.37,0:04:08.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看來像心臟病突發
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:09.89,0:04:12.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小心起見\N還是送去解剖鑑定一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:13.57,0:04:16.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這傢伙是個名人嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:16.53,0:04:20.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他一個星期有七個電視節目
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:20.29,0:04:22.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是一個受歡迎的笑星
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:23.41,0:04:24.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,說來可笑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:24.77,0:04:27.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他常用的題材是屍體
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:27.89,0:04:30.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒有人會為這個而笑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:32.61,0:04:34.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只是想賺人眼淚而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:39.09,0:04:40.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他…他是個好人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:42.69,0:04:45.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為甚麼…有人會他呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:47.01,0:04:51.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他是我認識的人中最好的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:54.29,0:04:58.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不能容忍\N像這樣來分散我們的小組…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:59.17,0:05:01.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,緒形先生在工作室裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:01.81,0:05:07.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他憤怒的狂熱者們正往那地點衝擊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:08.69,0:05:10.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可見他是多麼的受歡迎…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:12.53,0:05:20.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而且根據來源\N這件案子可能牽涉到有組織的犯罪…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:20.93,0:05:22.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,幹的好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:23.89,0:05:26.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我為那老婆婆感到難過
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:28.05,0:05:30.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,每天都有人死
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:33.17,0:05:34.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,到這邊來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:36.61,0:05:38.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我今天沒心情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:44.69,0:05:46.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這不像妳…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:48.13,0:05:49.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我知道…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:50.13,0:05:50.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只不過…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:53.17,0:05:53.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,砂羽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:55.25,0:05:58.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我實在不喜歡有人給我添麻煩…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:59.33,0:06:01.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,甚麼意思？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:03.25,0:06:04.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,感覺到嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:06.93,0:06:07.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,脫掉衣服吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:46.37,0:06:48.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,再準時一點，音分利
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:50.29,0:06:51.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要對誰下手？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:53.57,0:06:54.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哪一個？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:57.09,0:06:58.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他們全部
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:00.13,0:07:01.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們多叫了另一個人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:02.53,0:07:04.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你負責前面那個男人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:04.93,0:07:06.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,其餘的留給另一個人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:07.17,0:07:09.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他們幹了甚麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:09.73,0:07:12.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,兒童虐待狂…三個都是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:13.57,0:07:16.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他們將惡有惡報
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:35.57,0:07:38.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在我身邊…還有另一個人…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:00.29,0:08:03.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這個週末再來怎樣？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:03.49,0:08:05.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是的話，打電話給我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:06.21,0:08:07.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你知道我們的平常活動…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:08.53,0:08:10.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,妻子果然不夠好…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:55.57,0:08:56.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,吃驚嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:56.77,0:08:57.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,妳幹的？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:58.69,0:08:59.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:45.73,0:09:48.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,每個成年人\N得到的報酬總是一樣的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:48.61,0:09:50.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,待會兒凱尼那裡拿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:53.33,0:09:55.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你很臭，赤井先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:59.01,0:10:03.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,音分利\N你知道我的工作並不輕鬆啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:05.65,0:10:08.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,屍體的阿摩尼亞味\N總是讓我的眼淚流個不停
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:09.57,0:10:11.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那種腐爛的味道是那麼強烈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:13.17,0:10:15.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那怪不得我總是那麼臭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:37.49,0:10:38.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,赤井先生…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:39.09,0:10:41.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我之前的說話，你考慮了沒有？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:46.37,0:10:46.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:47.49,0:10:49.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不想阻礙你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:50.05,0:10:50.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,嗯…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:51.33,0:10:54.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你的慷慨大方讓我覺得不自在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:57.09,0:10:57.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只不過…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:58.29,0:11:00.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你得多負責三項工作
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:00.77,0:11:02.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我知道你會這麼說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:03.09,0:11:05.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這不是你我之間的事嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:06.13,0:11:08.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們得公平對待彼此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:09.41,0:11:10.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,凱尼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:10.45,0:11:11.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這沒錯吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:14.21,0:11:17.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,凱尼先生\N下次我會盡量準時的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:47.17,0:11:48.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你在幹甚麼啊？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:49.49,0:11:49.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你這豬
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:50.53,0:11:51.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你竟這麼慢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:54.29,0:11:55.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,蠢才
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:03.49,0:12:04.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,把它給我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:16.37,0:12:19.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,嘿，老兄，把球給我們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:23.09,0:12:24.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們弄髒了我的夾克
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:25.09,0:12:26.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,無論怎樣，它不是那麼好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:27.01,0:12:29.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,回去自己把它洗乾淨好嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:20.61,0:13:22.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那個人身手很好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:22.77,0:13:25.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以為甚麼我需要妳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:37.17,0:13:38.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,找你105元
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:38.85,0:13:40.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,謝謝光臨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:44.13,0:13:44.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,嘿！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:57.41,0:13:59.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你穿上那制服很好看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:59.81,0:14:00.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,妳…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:12.77,0:14:13.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,很好味
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:14.29,0:14:15.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,應該是新口味的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:16.93,0:14:17.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要吃嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:18.45,0:14:20.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,妳跟凱尼問我兼職的地點嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:24.13,0:14:24.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那麼…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:26.13,0:14:26.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,甚麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:27.81,0:14:30.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,告訴我妳的名字
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:31.17,0:14:31.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,砂羽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:34.05,0:14:37.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,代表 "握不住的砂子"\N和 "隨風飄的羽毛"
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:38.21,0:14:39.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要記好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:39.73,0:14:40.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那是妳的真名嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:41.65,0:14:42.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,當然
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:42.53,0:14:43.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:43.81,0:14:44.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,音分利
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:44.45,0:14:45.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,音分利君對吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:47.25,0:14:49.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,妳知道多少…我的事？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:50.45,0:14:51.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你生氣了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:51.81,0:14:53.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不是這樣…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:54.37,0:14:57.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,凱尼先生告訴我的只有這些
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:58.05,0:14:59.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,音分利君是真名嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:00.29,0:15:01.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:02.29,0:15:03.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是個不常見的名字
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:04.21,0:15:05.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大家都這樣說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:08.93,0:15:09.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你有家人嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:10.61,0:15:11.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:11.97,0:15:12.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,妳呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:14.45,0:15:15.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我也沒有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:17.09,0:15:19.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,很相似呢…我們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:24.05,0:15:25.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我也可以問妳嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:28.37,0:15:29.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:29.41,0:15:30.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,任何事情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:30.61,0:15:31.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我都告訴你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:57.25,0:15:59.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,赤井和妳是甚麼關係？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:00.77,0:16:01.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:03.17,0:16:05.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我的監護人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:07.65,0:16:09.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,和我一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:09.49,0:16:10.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,多奇怪的巧合…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:12.37,0:16:13.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們有著
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:37.33,0:17:39.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這耳環對妳很重要吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:41.73,0:17:42.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你怎麼知道？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:43.01,0:17:46.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我上次見到妳時，妳也戴著
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:51.09,0:17:54.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看起來很古怪，但真的很漂亮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:56.29,0:17:59.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是…我父母的血做成的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:05.57,0:18:10.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,算是我的護身符吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:15.57,0:18:16.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,走吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:17.73,0:18:18.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在哪兒？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:19.33,0:18:21.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,音分利君…的家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:56.61,0:18:57.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可惡…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:18.93,0:19:20.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這個人…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:20.45,0:19:22.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,妳認識他嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:22.53,0:19:24.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他是荷里活的電影明星\N對吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:25.41,0:19:27.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我有些同學是他的影迷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:28.69,0:19:30.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但我不知他有孿生兄弟…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:31.17,0:19:33.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,幾分鐘內他們會到這棟大廈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:35.81,0:19:37.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是第三位的名人呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:39.09,0:19:40.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,幹掉…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:40.61,0:19:41.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,右邊這個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:42.37,0:19:44.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果我殺錯人，可就抱歉了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:46.53,0:19:50.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他有三名保鑣，自己要小心點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:55.41,0:19:56.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,動手的地方呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:03.03,0:20:04.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們合作的真好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:04.93,0:20:08.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,全世界都以為我們是同一個人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:09.13,0:20:13.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,學院真該再特別給我們\N一個新的身分地位
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:13.93,0:20:16.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那我們就可以得兩座奧斯卡獎了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:16.95,0:20:19.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我想再下一步就是導演了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:19.65,0:20:23.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可以得很多的奧斯卡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:23.85,0:20:30.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不過\N如果沒得獎，我們可以買
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:42.85,0:20:44.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,妳他媽的是誰？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:53.25,0:20:54.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是個女的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:05.14,0:22:06.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,死吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:31.84,0:22:33.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,妳這爛貨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:38.24,0:22:39.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我要殺了妳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:27.04,0:23:28.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真精采呀，小殺手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:29.04,0:23:30.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不過妳玩完了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:35.52,0:23:37.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不准動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:43.02,0:23:44.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,甚麼鬼玩意？
